rows.label: tlk70000013_04_msg0001
rows.name:
I've been keeping my eye
on you lot. You really do
work hard, don't you?

rows.label: tlk70000013_04_msg0002
rows.name:
You probably work up big appetites,
eh? So why not stock up on lots of
supplies while you're here?

rows.label: tlk70000013_04_msg0003
rows.name:
If you fill your bellies with
lots of delicious food before
a fight, you're bound to win!

rows.label: tlk70000013_04_msg0004
rows.name:
I'll always have supplies for
you, so you come by as often
as you'd like, you hear?

rows.label: tlk70000013_04_msg0005
rows.name:
You've earned yourselves a
devoted old cheerleader in me!
